RELEASE INSTRUCTIONS - 1.16
This are the steps I followed to output Percolator release 1.16

0. BRANCH
  $ git clone git@github.com:percolator/percolator.git
  $ cd percolator
  $ git branch branch-1-16
  $ git checkout branch-1-16
  $ git push origin branch-1-16
  $ git checkout master
  $ git branch -f branch-1-16 origin/branch-1-16 #track branch
  $ git checkout branch-1-16

1. PACKAGES (64bit)
  (main) CMakeLists.txt: set(CPACK_PACKAGE_VERSION_MAJOR "1"), set(CPACK_PACKAGE_VERSION_MINOR "16"), set(TARGET_ARCH "amd64")
1.1. Packages (percolator + converters)
  run ./install/ubuntu_percolator_converters.sh
  $ cd /tmp/percolatorBuild
  $ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DGOOGLE_TEST=TRUE -DEXCLUDE_CONVERTERS=FALSE -DEXCLUDE_ELUDE=FALSE -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/bin -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=/tmp/xsd-3.3.0-x86_64-linux-gnu/ -DGOOGLE_TEST_PATH=/tmp/gtest-1.5.0 -DSCHEMA_LOCATION=/usr/share/percolator/xml-1-1 /scratch/temp/percolator
  $ make package
  
1.2. Packages (percolator only)
  repeat 1.1 with with -DEXCLUDE_CONVERTERS=TRUE

2. PACKAGES (32bit)
  repeat 1.1 and 1.2: set(TARGET_ARCH "i386")

3. SOURCE TARBALL
  repeat 1.1 with: $ make package_source

4. WIN EXECUTABLE
  to be run from appropriately configured machine: 
  $ ssh [someuser]@dirac.dbb.su.se
  $ ssh -l root -p 2222 localhost
  $ git clone git://github.com/percolator/percolator.git
  $ cd percolator
  $ run ./install/windows.sh
  to get it out of the virtual machine:
  $ scp -P 2222 root@dirac.dbb.su.se:/tmp/percolatorBuild/percolator-1.16.0-win32.exe ~/Desktop/

5. RELEASE
  upload generated files to https://github.com/percolator/percolator/downloads
  $ git tag -m 'Setting the rel-1-16 tag' rel-1-16 [commit_hash]
  $ git push --tags


You'll typically end up creating the following packages/executables:
percolator-1.15.0-win32.exe 			percolator + qvality + elude
percolator_converters-v1_15-src.tar.gz 		percolator + qvality + elude
percolator-v1_15-linux-amd64.deb 		percolator + qvality + elude
percolator-v1_15-linux-amd64.rpm 		percolator + qvality + elude
percolator-v1_15-linux-i386.deb 		percolator + qvality + elude
percolator-v1_15-linux-i386.rpm 		percolator + qvality + elude
percolator_converters-v1_15-linux-amd64.deb 	percolator (+ sqt2pin) + qvality + elude
percolator_converters-v1_15-linux-amd64.rpm 	percolator (+ sqt2pin) + qvality + elude
percolator_converters-v1_15-linux-i386.deb 	percolator (+ sqt2pin) + qvality + elude
percolator_converters-v1_15-linux-i386.rpm 	percolator (+ sqt2pin) + qvality + elude
